                    <solution>
                        <p>
                            We'd like to know the derivatives of more (elementary) functions; namely, we'd like to know
                            <me>
                                \frac{d}{dx}\left(\sin(x) \right), \frac{d}{dx}\left(\cos(x) \right), \frac{d}{dx}\left(e^x\right),
                                \frac{d}{dx}\left( \ln(x) \right)
                            </me>
                            
                        </p>
